A '''Jedi Initiate Clan''' was slaughtered by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] during his [[Operation: Knightfall/Legends|Raid on the Jedi Temple]] in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]. As the [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] of the [[501st Legion/Legends|501st Legion]] stormed the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]], they took refuge in the [[High Council Tower/Legends|High Council Tower]]. When Vader found them, they believed that he was attempting to protect them, asking what they should do. The newly-minted [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord]], however, killed them all. [[Sors Bandeam]] and [[Jeswi Ele]] were members.

